.Xr tftpd 8
.Pp
The default configuration of the TFTP server is to run in a 
.Xr chroot 8
environment in the
.Pa /tftpboot
directory.  Thus, the first order of business is to create this directory:
.(disp
.No # Ic "mkdir -p /tftpboot"
